+Default subprocess timeouts:
+
+| Phase | Default |
+|---|---|
+| handshake (`initialize`) | 5s |
+| `emit` | 30s |
+| `shutdown` | 5s |
+
+These are runtime defaults, not negotiated wire fields. Per-method
+overrides are reserved for future work.
